casebody.data:
No. 10-7576. Ernest Miller, Petitioner v. California. 562 U.S. 1175, 131 S. Ct. 1015,

178 L. Ed. 2d 822,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 677. January 18, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of California dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
